<h2 class="red">SUMMER DANCE CLASSES<br /><span style="font-size: small; color: #000000;"><strong>Ballet - Jazz - Contemporary - Tap - Hip Hop - Break Dance - Preschool Ballet/Tap - Mommy &amp; Me</strong>&nbsp;</span></h2>
