<h2 class="red">SUMMER MUSIC LESSONS<br /><span style="font-size: small; color: #000000;"><strong>Piano - Voice - Guitar - Bass - Violin - Drums - Guitar Jr - Piano/Voice Combo</strong>&nbsp;</span></h2>
<hr />
<p>Most students spend the first 2 months of fall reviewing what they have forgotten over summer! Why not take a few summer lessons to keep up your skill or even try a new instrument? Our school offers flexible private music lessons for all ages. Summer Session runs July 7 - Aug. 16.</p>
<p>Let us know the weeks you&rsquo;re out of town when you register and we&rsquo;ll accommodate you with alternate lesson times for unlimited make-ups in the summer. Hours vary Mon-Fri 2pm-8pm, and Sat 9am-2pm.</p>
